  <para>
    The <guimenuitem>Xtns</guimenuitem> menu gets its somewhat cryptic
    name from the term, <quote>Extensions</quote>.  Accordingly, you will
    find various commands for managing extensions (also known as
    <quote>plug-ins</quote>) and for accessing scripts here.
  </para>
